data.description: !!Back on the market!!  Buyer's financing fell through.  290 Cresthaven is just waiting for you to move in and make it your own!  Fantastic floor plan, great private outdoor space, unfinished basement where your imagination has ample space to grow, and even an upstairs laundry!  The neighborhood is an established gem, where this home sits on the end of the street and backs up to a huge vegetable farm.  You will have plenty of privacy, but also the convenience of being only minutes away from all your shopping needs, downtown Chambersburg, and Interstate 81. CALL ME TODAY FOR YOUR SHOWING!!!!!
